						               													<description>Instant excitement. Easy-to-play pocket size. Lightning-quick, baseball action in a fast-paced dice game based on America's #1 past time, baseball!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Action Dice Baseball is a head-to-head dice game that can be played individually, or two players.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;This dice strategy game can take you 9 innings! Steal bases, errors, home runs and more.  It's fast, easy to learn and you call the plays. Perfect for tailgating at games, at the home or in your office, or while traveling on airplanes -- play it anywhere! Results in the MLB can happen in this game. Get a hit, roll the dice and instantly see the results!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;This game can be single or two players. To play the game simply choose one of the 3 swings and roll the dice to see the result. 9 innings of baseball where each team can hit, steal and bunt for scores. Contact swings, power and bunting will get you on base then it's up to you if you choose to steal bases to increase your chance to score!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Keeping track of time in this baseball game is easy. Provided are score sheets. Each team gets 3 outs per inning just like pro baseball. After 9 innings are completed, the final score will determine the winning team. The team with the most goals wins the game. If the score is tied then extra innings begin.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the publisher&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
